io.confluent.ksql.physical.scalablepush

Class PushPhysicalPlan

  • java.lang.Object
    • io.confluent.ksql.physical.scalablepush.PushPhysicalPlan

  • public class PushPhysicalPlan
extends java.lang.Object
    Represents a physical plan for a scalable push query. The execution of the plan is done async on a Context so that running queries don't need to use dedicated threads. This is especially important since push queries tend to be long-running. This should allow scalable push queries to have many concurrent requests.
